    {
      "id": "PopularPost193294",
      "post_content": "Okay, I'll be the slack-jawed jerk and mention [Doubling Season](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Doubling Season). Lets you cycle through your library; {1}: Draw a card, then discard a card.  \n  \nA good enabler, of course in the Legacy games you'll do that in, you can do far better. Perhaps it could be a Modern engine. But there isn't that much of a reason to have cards in your graveyard in Modern, since there's no good reanimation in the format...",
      "posted_by": "BegleOne",
