    {
      "id": "PopularPost118163",
      "post_content": "I just love the design of this guy. He's very playable, as he can serve as a discard outlet, a card drawing engine, and a fatty all on the same card. In any deck where your graveyard matters, he is a great utility. The activation costs never bothered me, keeps him from being the first [Arcbound Ravager](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Arcbound Ravager)... Note that it is free to remove his counters in response to removal. ",
      "posted_by": "Kryptnyt",
