      "post_content": "@Omenchild: This is the second comment of yours i don't like. After the one i read about [Cursed Scroll](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Cursed Scroll), anything you say is completely discredited. I think what themicronaut is trying to say is that madness would work well witht this, not that it is your key IDEAL card to use for madness. Everyone knows you can do 15 damage on turn 2 with [Wild Mongrel](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Wild Mongrel), thats great, but this card is fun.\n  \n   \nI love this card, something about it, i just love using craatures with multiple interactive abilities. Also, madness is no longer a competitive deck so therefore this card is perfect for casual play, which is the only place madess is played anymore.\n  \n   \nThis card would work well with recurrsion too.",
